  "title": "6 Months Contract Assistant Manager, Corporate Sustainability_BJJ",
  "description": "<p>6 Months Contract Assistant Manager, Corporate Sustainability</p><p><br />Our client is a bank.</p><p><br />Job Description:</p><p>•\tDevelop and manage the social impact programmes which align with the company’s sustainability focus and commitments</p><p>•\tOversee the company’s volunteering activities and fund-raising initiatives</p><p>•\tInitiate and develop collaborations with relevant government agencies, non-profit organisations, and other community stakeholders, to achieve desired outcomes and impact.</p><p>•\tWork with internal committee to drive volunteer engagement and recognition</p><p>•\tCollaborate closely with stakeholders to drive external and internal communication to raise awareness on social impact topics, programmes and events</p><p><br />Job Requirements:</p><p>•\tDiploma or Degree in any relevant discipline</p><p>•\t4 to 6 years of Events Management experience</p><p>•\tSalary ranges between S$4,000 to S$6,000 per month</p><p><br />Please send your application directly via janntan@recruitexpress.com.sg for a faster response.</p><p><br />Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br />(Jann) Tan Wei Ying (R1103708)</p><p>Email Address: janntan@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p>Recruiter's Ref Code: #BJJ</p>",
